Text: nov support Cc In general everything went ok today Nov Susan Scott had some problems with some of the excel spreadsheets shes been running on her machine The issue here is that the CopyFromRecordset method of a range object is failing The simple fix is to use a user defined function named rsOutput instead of the method She also mentioned that a process that outputs a text file to the E drive seems to be failing on her machine but is working fine on Dutch Quigleys machine Shell provide more detail to support on Monday Cheers EdII
